name: Aqua Story - Super Oxidizer!
text: Send up to 2 "Aquarium" cards you control to the GY; Special Summon "Aquaactress monsters from your hand or Deck with different names equal to the amount you sent. You cannot Summon monsters the turn you activate this card except "Aquaactress" monsters. You can only activate 1 "Aqua Story - Super Oxidizer!" per turn.
